title: In-Process And Final Quality Engineer
description: Learn quality engineering processes including in-process and final quality inspection techniques.
jobDescription: Responsible for ensuring product quality through in-process and final inspection procedures.
eligibilityCriteria: Diploma (after 10th) in Electrical, Electronics, or Mechanical Engineering with 1 year of relevant work experience
12th Grade Pass with 1 year of NTC/NAC and 1 year of relevant work experience

10th Grade Pass with 4 years of relevant work experience
